":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T13:11:42.000Z","msg":"四期支那車出軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57a82efe34651f3a06d9928b050e30a6f1457bb1","tid":2179932,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T13:13:08.000Z","msg":"剛剛踩正波口，614P 615P 505收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73d6e9a26e7193175d96a4b8dabf8e89267d6198","tid":2179932,"uid":51271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T13:16:42.000Z","msg":"唔計果次所謂超速出軌，四期支那車試車果時出過一次軌，呢次第二次"},{"pid":"32c8374065a39c801b4a70c98b4c9e9ee6ed1890","tid":2179932,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T13:21:11.000Z","msg":"輕鐵路綫改道如下：<br />\n<br />\n614綫往元朗方向改道，將不停杯渡站至鳳地站；<br />\n<br />\n614P綫往兆康方向改道，將不停杯渡站至兆康站；<br />\n<br />\n615P綫往屯門碼頭方向改道，將不停兆康站至麒麟站。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n港鐵免費接駁巴士將於稍後時間到達，乘客請考慮使用其他交通工具。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n港鐵職員正在處理事件。<br />\n<br />\n不便之處，敬請原諒。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黨鐵又跌錢比狗巴"},{"pid":"8d25214c58f6c537f433f058e8e6968775c1878d","tid":2179932,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T13:22:35.000Z","msg":"兆康站個6號月台終於開封，然後屯門醫院之間果幾個波口終於有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/